videos.description: Stanford's Jay Tyler lets a punt go right through his hands before it's recovered by Johnny Den Bleyker to set up UCLA in the red zone.
videos.headline: UCLA recovers dropped punt

videos.description: UCLA RB Soso Jamabo takes the hand off and rushes 49 yards down to the Stanford 30-yard line.
videos.headline: Jamabo rushes 49 yards for UCLA first down

videos.description: Josh Rosen finds Darren Andrews open in the end zone for the first UCLA touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Rosen connects with Andrews for the UCLA TD

videos.description: Stanford RB Bryce Love rushes all the way down to the UCLA two-yard line after a 32-yard rush.
videos.headline: Love sets up Stanford after 32-yard run

videos.description: Cameron Scarlett takes the hand off and dives straight over the offensive line for the Cardinal touchdown.
videos.headline: Stanford's Scarlett dives into end zone for TD

videos.description: Stanford quarterback K.J. Costello rolls out and dives into the corner of the end zone breaking the plane while taking a big hit.
videos.headline: Costello lays out for the Stanford TD

videos.description: Stanford head coach David Shaw talks about his quarterback's first-half performance and how he plans to stop Josh Rosen going forward.
videos.headline: Shaw thinks Costello is playing "gritty"

videos.description: Stanford CB Alijah Holder is ejected for targeting after a hit on UCLA receiver Eldridge Massington.
videos.headline: Stanford's Holder ejected for targeting

videos.description: Soso Jamabo ducks below the offensive line and gets into the end zone off the three-yard touchdown rush.
videos.headline: UCLA punches it in at the goal line

videos.description: Connor Wedington on the reverse rushes all the way down to the UCLA 19-yard line on a 43-yard run.
videos.headline: Wedington takes reverse down to red zone for Cardinal

videos.description: K.J. Costello throws to the corner of the end zone to Trenton Irwin who fights off two defenders for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Costello finds Irwin for the Stanford TD

videos.description: UCLA receiver Christian Pabico has the ball stripped from him by Stanford defenders who recover the ensuing fumble.
videos.headline: Stanford strips ball on group tackle

videos.description: Cameron Scarlett dives over the top of the offensive line to score another Stanford touchdown.
videos.headline: Scarlett scores another leaping goal-line TD

videos.description: Josh Rosen throws to Jordan Lasley over the middle who takes it 39 yards for a Bruins touchdown.
videos.headline: Rosen with the 39-yard TD to Lasley

videos.description: Bryce Love with a 30-yard rush sets up Stanford at the UCLA four-yard line.
videos.headline: Love takes Stanford down to the goal line

videos.description: After review it is determined Dalton Schultz makes the touchdown catch off the pass from K.J. Costello.
videos.headline: Stanford's Schultz scoops pass  for TD

videos.description: Josh Rosen throws to the back corner of the end zone to Eldridge Massington for the UCLA touchdown.
videos.headline: UCLA scores on another Rosen TD

videos.description: Bryce Love takes the handoff and rushes 69 yards for another Stanford touchdown.
videos.headline: Love goes 69 yards for the Stanford TD

videos.description: Stanford RB Bryce Love talks about his huge game on the ground and praises his teammates for their part.
videos.headline: Love gives credit to teammates for big game
